e County areas since getting started in 1997, and love to support the local tech community and events. We&#8217;re involved in sponsoring MuckerLab, and regularly host &#8230; <a rel="nofollow" target="_blank" href="http://2012.la.wordcamp.org/09/13/sponsor-spotlight-dreamhost/">Continue reading <span class="meta-nav">&#8594;</span></a>";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:4:"guid";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:35:"http://2012.la.wordcamp.org/?p=1073";s:7:"attribs";a:1:{s:0:"";a:1:{s:11:"isPermaLink";s:5:"false";}}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:7:"pubDate";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:31:"Thu, 13 Sep 2012 19:44:57 +0000";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:8:"category";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:8:"Sponsors";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:40:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/";a:1:{s:7:"encoded";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:2420:"<p>DreamHost is proud to sponsor WordCamp LA!   We&#8217;ve been based in the<br />\nLA and Orange County areas since getting started in 1997, and love to<br />\nsupport the local tech community and events.  We&#8217;re involved in<br />\nsponsoring MuckerLab, and regularly host meetups at our offices,<br />\nincluding WordPress SoCal and OpenStack LA.</p>\n<p>WordPress is a BIG deal at DreamHost.  We host over 600,000 WordPress<br />\ndomains, and offer a cool One-Click Installer, along with Automatic<br />\nUpgrades, if you want them.</p>\n<p>DreamHost is also a big contributor to open source, and the WordPress<br />\ncommunity in general.  We&#8217;ve recently hired Mika Epstein (@ipstenu) to<br />\nfurther our quest in WordPress Support Awesomeness (pending ^tm), and<br />\ncontinue to contribute to the WordPress core and other projects, like<br />\nwp-cli and OpenStack.  You can see our contributions to W