(9, 1, '2012-12-06 04:19:43', '2012-12-06 04:19:43', '<h4><i>We like to describe ourselves as smart, innovative, and efficient.</i></h4>\r\n\r\nFirst Capitol Consulting, Inc. is made up of tax professionals from the "Big 4" accounting firms that provide consistent and state-of-the-art tax services. Our TaxAdvantagesm service was developed in partnership with Intuit to serve 1.4 million companies with an unlimited number of employees to provide credits and incentives services.\r\n\r\nCurrently, First Capitol Consulting, Inc. is a strategic partner with McGladrey, and is the preferred Work Opportunity Tax Credit service provider of Grant Thornton. First Capitol Consulting, Inc. is recognized as the industry leader in every aspect: reputation, performance, audit, experience and expertise.', 'About Us', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'about-us', '', '', '2012-12-27 00:31:34', '2012-12-27 00:31:34', '', 72, 'http://10.0.1.22:8888/fcci/?page_id=9', 1, 'page', '', 0),
