(14, 1, '2012-12-06 04:25:11', '2012-12-06 04:25:11', '<h4><i>Because you deserve the expertise and communication required to manage the multistage,\r\ntime-sensitive federal and state tax credit claims.</i></h4>\r\n\r\n<p>TaxAdvantagesm streamlines the credit generation process by combining federal and state tax\r\ncredit capture. Through consolidation, TaxAdvantage<sup>sm</sup> offers:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>The capture of time-sensitive overlapping state and federal tax credits.</li>\r\n<li>Reduced client overhead.</li>\r\n<li>Better coordination and direct communication with our senior tax professionals through\r\nour web portal.</li>\r\n<li>Representation with the IRS and state taxing authorities by tax professionals from the\r\n"Big 4" accounting firms.</li>\r\n<li>Maximized state tax credits via utilization of the web portal, web integration and call\r\ncenter data capture.</li>\r\n</ul>', 'Why sign up?', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'open', '', 'why-sign-up', '', '', '2012-12-27 00:33:54', '2012-12-27 00:33:54', '', 72, 'http://10.0.1.22:8888/fcci/?page_id=14', 3, 'page', '', 0),
