(16, 1, '2012-12-06 04:25:11', '2012-12-06 04:25:11', 'Effectively claiming and managing federal and state tax credits are a multistage, time-sensitive process requiring expertise and communication.\r\n\r\nTaxAdvantagesm streamlines the credit generation process by combining federal and state tax credit capture.\r\n\r\nThrough consolidation, TaxAdvantagesm offers…\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Capture of time-sensitive overlapping state and federal tax credits</li>\r\n	<li>Reduced client overhead</li>\r\n	<li>Better coordination and communication through our web portal and direct contact with our senior tax professionals.</li>\r\n	<li>Representation with the IRS and state taxing authorities by tax professionals from the “Big 4” accounting firms</li>\r\n	<li>Maximize state tax credits via utilization of web portal, web integration and call center data capture.</li>\r\n</ul>', 'Why sign up?', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '14-revision-2', '', '', '2012-12-06 04:25:11', '2012-12-06 04:25:11', '', 14, 'http://10.0.1.22:8888/fcci/14-revision-2/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(17, 1, '2012-12-06 04:26:19', '2012-12-06 04:26:19', '<h4><i>Simple. Scalable. Mobile.</i></h4>\r\n\r\nFirst Capitol Consulting, Inc. brings you "big firm" expertise, combined with a personal level of service you need and deserve.\r\n\r\nWe all know that earning tax credits and incentives is not an easy task. Even though many accountants and business owners know about them, few are able to claim tax credits to the fullest extent because of the subject area knowledge that is required to negotiate all the bureaucratic hurdles thrown your way. We focus solely on tax credits and incentives, which means we are completely focused on optimizing clients’ tax benefits.\r\n\r\nOur entire team is dedicated to maximizing credit generation. We maintain a diverse client portfolio ranging from small, single owner businesses to national Fortune 500 companies; we help businesses of all sizes and types. At the same time, our team is comprised of professionals from the "Big 4" accounting firms. Hence, we offer the highest level of expertise and experience. The tax credit generating process is specialized, which generally deters businesses from utilizing such programs. Moreover, generating credits requires consistent managing, long-term oversight and maintenance. Non-specialists are not able to compete with our expertise to effectively generate tax credits.\r\n\r\nFirst Capitol Consulting, Inc. can ensure you are getting all of the government sanctioned tax benefits your business earns with minimal involvement for you or your accountant.', 'TaxAdvantage<sup>sm</sup> &dash; Competitive Edge', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'open', '', 'taxadvantagesm-competitive-edge', '', '', '2012-12-27 04:49:41', '2012-12-27 04:49:41', '', 72, 'http://10.0.1.22:8888/fcci/?page_id=17', 9, 'page', '', 0),
