(32, 1, '2012-12-06 04:43:00', '2012-12-06 04:43:00', 'First Capitol Consulting, Inc. is a leader in providing tax incentive programs nationwide.\r\nTax incentive programs are offered by most states and local jurisdictions to businesses based on geographic locations, hiring, and/or expenditures. Determining whether a tax incentive applies in a certain jurisdiction is a laborious process involving collecting applicable data, screening employees, researching records, and communicating with local and state government agencies. Furthermore, these programs are constantly evolving with the passage of new legislations.  First Capitol Consulting services include providing the most comprehensive tax incentive program available in your jurisdiction. First Capitol Consulting will handle all of the research and data analysis and also ensure that all appropriate and lucrative tax incentives are available to your business. Some of these programs may provide thousands to multi-millions in tax credits and refunds.', 'Multi State Tax Programs', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'multi-state-tax-programs', '', '', '2012-12-06 04:59:37', '2012-12-06 04:59:37', '', 48, 'http://10.0.1.22:8888/fcci/?page_id=32', 2, 'page', '', 0),
