(85, 1, '2012-12-06 17:45:19', '2012-12-06 17:45:19', '<h2>Overview</h2>\r\nFirst Capitol Consulting, Inc. is made up of of lawyers, CPAs and tax professionals that have\r\ndeveloped strong relationships with the taxing authorities. We produce the highest quality\r\nwork and are recognized as the industry experts representing companies in audits, appeals,\r\nsettlements and hearings. By doing so, we have demonstrated our expertise and recognition as\r\nthe industry leader.\r\n\r\n<h2>Company Profile</h2>\r\nA manufacturer with an annual gross sale of $150 million per annum. During its exam, the auditor denied $1.2 million in tax credits that were originally generated by a consultant with no license to practice tax.\r\n\r\n<h2>Tax Savings</h2>\r\nThe company contacted First Capitol Consulting, Inc. to assist with its audit. We represented the\r\ncompany and generated over $2.5 million in tax credits to offset any disallowed tax credits and\r\nincreased its refunds.', 'IRS and State Taxing Authorities Represenation', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'irs-and-state-taxing-authorities-represenation', '', '', '2012-12-25 23:09:42', '2012-12-25 23:09:42', '', 37, 'http://10.0.1.22:8888/fcci/?page_id=85', 2, 'page', '', 0),
