(87, 1, '2012-12-06 17:46:03', '2012-12-06 17:46:03', '<h2>Overview</h2>\r\n\r\nFirst Capitol Consulting, Inc. developed TaxAdvantage<sup>sm</sup> with Intuit to serve 1.4 million small to\r\nmid-sized companies. Our working knowledge of small to mid-sized businesses is unparalleled in\r\nthe industry. We completely understand the needs and limited resources that most small to midsized\r\ncompanies have. Hence, our implementation process requires very limited participation by\r\nits clients.\r\n<h2>Company Profile</h2>\r\n\r\nA small apparel manufacturer that was established in 1971 and has 67 employees. In 2008, the\r\ncompany lost several major retail accounts resulting in inventory pile-up and liquidity crisis.\r\n<h2>Tax Savings</h2>\r\n\r\nA First Capitol Consulting, Inc.''s account executive, who specializes in small to mid-sized companies, deployed single point of contact with the company. We initiated its five year look-back\r\n"Feasibility Study" and upon implementation, the company obtained refunds in excess of $300,000, which was a much needed cash infusion to the company that was hemorrhaging due to lack of cash-flow.', 'Small & Mid-Sized Businesss', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'small-mid-sized-businesss', '', '', '2012-12-25 23:11:33', '2012-12-25 23:11:33', '', 37, 'http://10.0.1.22:8888/fcci/?page_id=87', 3, 'page', '', 0),
