(89, 1, '2012-12-06 17:46:34', '2012-12-06 17:46:34', '<h2>Overview</h2>\r\n\r\nFirst Capitol Consulting, Inc. understands the workings and needs of tech companies. In a partnership with Intuit, we developed a proprietary software and web portal. We understand tech company initiatives, personnel, and very specific needs.\r\n\r\n<h2>Company Profile</h2>\r\n\r\nIndustry leader and Fortune 500 company that is expanding to other states and countries. Due to its rapid growth, the company used temporary work source via third party temporary workforce agency to meet its rapid growth.\r\n\r\n<h2>Tax Savings</h2>\r\n\r\nFirst Capitol Consulting, Inc.''s understanding of tech company operations and hiring practices led to capturing tax credits that were previously overlooked by other credits and incentive providers. By implementing its strategy, we increased federal credits and quadrupled state tax credits, lowering the effective tax rate from 33% to 27.5%.', 'Tech Companies', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'tech-companies', '', '', '2012-12-27 04:08:06', '2012-12-27 04:08:06', '', 37, 'http://10.0.1.22:8888/fcci/?page_id=89', 4, 'page', '', 0),
