(93, 1, '2012-12-06 17:47:22', '2012-12-06 17:47:22', '<h2>Overview</h2>\r\n\r\nFirst Capitol Consulting, Inc. has strong presence in the automotive industry. We currently represent a regional automotive company with over $2.5 billion in assets.\r\n\r\n<h2>Company Profile</h2>\r\n\r\nAs one of the fastest growing automotive companies in the country, this company needed assistance with federal tax credit programs. They were very disenchanted with their prior service provider''s antiquated process, non-intuitive methodology and lack of tax knowledge.\r\n\r\n<h2>Tax Savings</h2>\r\n\r\nFirst Capitol Consulting, Inc. utilized its call-center and web integrated portal to capture federal tax credits. Our process resulted in a 147% increase in hiring tax credits compared to previous year completed by a publicly traded tax credit company.', 'Automotive', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'automotive', '', '', '2012-12-27 04:05:14', '2012-12-27 04:05:14', '', 37, 'http://10.0.1.22:8888/fcci/?page_id=93', 6, 'page', '', 0),
