(95, 1, '2012-12-06 17:47:43', '2012-12-06 17:47:43', '<h2>Overview</h2>\r\n\r\nFirst Capitol Consulting, Inc. currently represents over 3,000 franchise chain restaurants in the U.S. We work very close with payroll companies to accomplish high compliance rates and have a deep understanding of employee scheduling complexities.\r\n\r\n<h2>Company Profile</h2>\r\n\r\nA Salt Lake City, Utah-based fast food chain operator, with rapid growth in Texas and Nevada. The company has acquired over 50 locations per quarter.\r\n\r\n<h2>Tax Savings</h2>\r\n\r\nFirst Capitol Consulting, Inc. utilized its call-center, payroll integration, "best practices" webinars, quarterly management meetings, and weekly compliance report to accomplish 92% WOTC compliance result. This is in light of the company with 300% turnover per annum.', 'Franchise Chain Restaurants', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'franchise-chain-restaurants', '', '', '2012-12-26 01:25:30', '2012-12-26 01:25:30', '', 37, 'http://10.0.1.22:8888/fcci/?page_id=95', 7, 'page', '', 0),
