(106, 1, '2012-12-06 17:55:20', '2012-12-06 17:55:20', 'Overview\r\n\r\nFirst Capitol Consulting developed TaxAdvantagesm with Intuit to serve 1.4 million small to mid-sized companies.  Its working knowledge of small to mid-sized businesses is unparalleled in the industry.  First Capitol Consulting understands the needs and limited resources of small to mid-sized companies.  Hence, First Capitol Consulting implementation process requires very limited participation by its clients. \r\n\r\nCompany Profile\r\n\r\nA small apparel manufacturer established in 1971 with 30 employees.  Although lost many major retail clients, the company started to establish itself back in the market place by creating innovative fashion design.\r\n\r\nTax Savings\r\n\r\nA First Capitol Consulting’s account executive, who specializes in small to mid-sized companies, deployed single point of contact with the company.  Utilizing First Capitol Consulting’s vast network of CPAs and payroll companies, First Capitol Consulting obtained refunds in excess of $200,000, a much needed cash infusion to the company as it needed capital to build inventory based on its new fashion designs.', 'Small & Mid-Sized Businesss', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '87-revision-2', '', '', '2012-12-06 17:55:20', '2012-12-06 17:55:20', '', 87, 'http://10.0.1.22:8888/fcci/87-revision-2/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
