(110, 1, '2012-12-06 18:11:47', '2012-12-06 18:11:47', '<h4><i>This is how we do it.</i></h4>\r\n<img src="http://10.0.1.19:8888/fcci/wp-content/uploads/2012/12/process-overall.png" alt="process-overall" width="630"/>\r\n<ol>\r\n<li>We collect all the necessary documents for your business, Federal and State.</li>\r\n<li>We do all the required paperwork.</li>\r\n<li>We work directly with your tax preparer to deliver the information you need to use these tax\r\ncredits.</li>\r\n<li>You save money on your taxes.</li>\r\n<li>No upfront or hidden costs. Ever.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n*We guarantee any and all credits accumulated through our work. We represent you in the case of an audit, unlike payroll companies and other competitors.', 'Overall Process', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'overall-process', '', '', '2012-12-27 04:44:44', '2012-12-27 04:44:44', '', 107, 'http://10.0.1.22:8888/fcci/?page_id=110', 1, 'page', '', 0),
