(249, 1, '2012-12-18 06:08:22', '2012-12-18 06:08:22', '<h4>Value Added Service</h4>\r\n\r\nWith our experience and expertise working with Intuit Employee Management Services, we\r\nbring rich institutional expertise to market. Our system will integrate with your payroll software to\r\nensure maximum tax savings to your clients that is immediate, seamless, and efficient.\r\n\r\nOur partnership with Intuit creates a synergy of services that will benefit your clients. By\r\ncombining payroll and HR with employee tax credit, the cost savings alone will exceed costs\r\nassociated with payroll offerings.\r\n\r\nIn short, working with First Capitol Consulting, Inc. will set your company apart from competitors\r\nby improving your clients’ bottom line. ', 'Payroll & PEO Companies', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'payroll-peo-companies', '', '', '2012-12-25 22:54:18', '2012-12-25 22:54:18', '', 188, 'http://10.0.1.19:8888/fcci/?page_id=249', 2, 'page', '', 0),
