(260, 1, '2012-12-18 06:16:09', '2012-12-18 06:16:09', 'The CAEZ has been in existence since 1984, and has generally low awareness about the program. Due to eligible areas changing over time, the Government has not done a good job keeping business owners apprised of all the changes.\r\n\r\nEnacted in 1977, as the Targeted Job Tax Credit. (PL 95-30) was renewed by the Work Opportunity Tax Credit Act. (PL 104-188) in 1996.\r\n\r\nFirst Capitol Consulting tax counsel is dedicated to updates and promoting these programs in local, state and national levels.', 'Why haven''t I heard of CAEZ, WOTC or any of the other tax credit programs before?', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'why-havent-i-heard-of-caez-wotc-or-any-of-the-other-tax-credit-programs-before', '', '', '2012-12-26 01:32:21', '2012-12-26 01:32:21', '', 0, 'http://10.0.1.19:8888/fcci/?post_type=faqs&#038;p=260', 1, 'faqs', '', 0),
