(356, 1, '2012-12-23 20:00:59', '2012-12-23 20:00:59', '<h2>Overview</h2>\r\n\r\nFirst Capitol Consulting, consisting of lawyers, CPAs and tax professionals, have developed strong relationships with the taxing authorities by producing the highest quality work and being recognized as the industry experts.  First Capitol Consulting has represented companies in audits, appeals, settlements and hearings.  By doing so, First Capitol Consulting demonstrated its expertise and is  recognized as the industry leader.  \r\n\r\n<h2>Company Profile</h2>\r\n\r\nA manufacturer with an annual gross sale of $150 million per annum.  During its exam, $1,2 million tax credits, generated by credits and incentives company with no licensed individual, were denied by the auditor.  \r\n\r\n<h2>Tax Savings</h2>\r\n\r\nThe company contacted First Capitol Consulting to assist with its audit.  First Capitol Consulting represented the company and generated over $2.5 million in tax credits to offset any disallowed tax credits and increase its refunds.', 'IRS and State Taxing Authorities Represenation', 'First Capitol Consulting, consisting of lawyers, CPAs and tax professionals, have developed strong relationships with the taxing authorities by producing the highest quality work and being recognized as the industry experts', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'irs-and-state-taxing-authorities-represenation', '', '', '2012-12-24 18:44:48', '2012-12-24 18:44:48', '', 0, 'http://10.0.1.19:8888/fcci/?post_type=case-study&#038;p=356', 1, 'case-study', '', 0),
