(361, 1, '2012-12-23 20:01:25', '2012-12-23 20:01:25', '<h2>Overview</h2>\r\n\r\nFirst Capitol Consulting understands the workings and needs of high-tech companies.  First Capitol Consulting, in a partnership with Intuit, developed its proprietary software and its web-portal.  First Capitol Consulting understands the high-tech company inititiatives, personnel and very specific needs.\r\n\r\n<h2>Company Profile</h2>\r\n\r\nIndustry leader and Fortune 500 company, expanding to other states and countries.  Due to its rapid growth, the company utilized temp work source for growth.\r\n\r\n<h2>Tax Savings</h2>\r\n\r\nFirst Capitol Consulting’s understanding of high-tech company operations and hiring practices led to capturing tax credits that were previously overlooked by other credits and incentive providers.  By implementing its strategy, First Capitol Consulting increased federal credits and quadrupled state tax credits.', 'High – Tech Companies', 'First Capitol Consulting understands the workings and needs of high-tech companies.  First Capitol Consulting, in a partnership with Intuit, developed its proprietary software and its web-portal', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'high-tech-companies', '', '', '2012-12-24 18:45:06', '2012-12-24 18:45:06', '', 0, 'http://10.0.1.19:8888/fcci/?post_type=case-study&#038;p=361', 3, 'case-study', '', 0),
