(398, 1, '2012-12-23 20:01:54', '2012-12-23 20:01:54', '<h2>Overview</h2>\r\n\r\nFirst Capitol Consulting has strong prescence in automotive industry.  First Capitol Consulting currently works with an automotive company with over 1.2 billion in assets.\r\n\r\n<h2>Company Profile</h2>\r\n\r\nAs one of the fastest growing automotive company in the country, the company needed assistance with federal tax credit programs.  \r\n\r\n<h2>Tax Savings</h2>\r\n\r\nFirst Capitol Consulting utilized its call-center and web integrated portal to capture federal tax credits.  First Capitol Consulting process resulted in 47% increase in hiring tax credit compared to previously completed by a publicly traded tax credit company.', 'Automative', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '365-revision-2', '', '', '2012-12-23 20:01:54', '2012-12-23 20:01:54', '', 365, 'http://10.0.1.19:8888/fcci/365-revision-2/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(399, 1, '2012-12-23 20:02:06', '2012-12-23 20:02:06', '<h2>Overview</h2>\r\n\r\nFirst Capitol Consulting currently represents over 3,000 franchise chain restaurants in the U.S.  First Capitol Consulting works very closely with payroll companies to accomplish high compliance rate and has deep understanding of employee scheduling complexities.\r\n\r\n<h2>Company Profile</h2>\r\n\r\nSalt Lake City, Utah based fast food chain operator with rapid growth in Texas and Nevada.  The company acquired over 30 locations per annum.\r\n\r\n<h2>Tax Savings</h2>\r\n\r\nFirst Capitol Consulting utilized its call-center, payroll integration, “best practices” webinars, quarterly management meetings and weekly compliance report to accomplish 92% WOTC compliance result.  This is in light of the company with 300% turnover per annum.', 'Franchise Chain Restaurants', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '367-revision-2', '', '', '2012-12-23 20:02:06', '2012-12-23 20:02:06', '', 367, 'http://10.0.1.19:8888/fcci/367-revision-2/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
