(447, 1, '2012-12-06 17:36:34', '2012-12-06 17:36:34', 'Tax Incentive Specialists Since 1999\r\n\r\nFounded in 1999, First Capitol Consulting has attracted and benefited thousands of clients, including international and national brands, fortune 500 companies and small to mid-sized businesses.  \r\n\r\nThe professional staff at First Capitol Consulting is comprised of tax professionals from the "Big 4" accounting firms. First Capitol Consulting was created in order to provide more personalized, focused, and consistent professional services than what is possible at the “Big 4” accounting firms. \r\n\r\nWe believe that the need to be successful is universal, but how each client gets there is unique. First Capitol Consulting does not offer its services with just a one-size-fits-all attitude. We forge a personalized relationship with each of our clients and commit to fully understanding your industry and special needs. This allows us to ensure that your tax incentive program is tailored to your unique situation provide you with the highest amounts of tax credits available to you.\r\n\r\nTo maintain our competitive edge, in 2008, we partnered with Intuit to co-develop our proprietary web platform, IT solutions, call-center, and combined them with our tax professionals to implement Work Opportunity Tax Credit (WOTC) and California Enterprise Zone (CAEZ) tax programs.  The TaxAdvantagesm web portal provides client with online employee screening capability and up-to-date information on their credit program.  This process is built to handle over 1.4 million companies with unlimited number of employees in a transparent, robust and user friendly environment.  TaxAdvantagesm is scalable, simple, and free of upfront or hidden costs.', 'Why TaxAdvantage<sup>SM</sup>', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '11-revision-5', '', '', '2012-12-06 17:36:34', '2012-12-06 17:36:34', '', 11, 'http://10.0.1.19:8888/fcci/11-revision-5/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
