(507, 1, '2012-12-24 21:01:14', '2012-12-24 21:01:14', '<h2>Overview</h2>\r\n\r\nFirst Capitol Consulting, with tax professionals from the “Big 4’ accounting firms, understands, not just credits and incentives, but intricacies and pit-falls of merging two national brands.  First Capitol Consulting assisted merger of one of the oldest cosmetic companies in the world.\r\n\r\n<h2>Company Profile</h2>\r\n\r\nIndustry leader and well recognized national brand in cosmetics acquired by a foreign international company.\r\n\r\n<h2>Tax Savings</h2>\r\n\r\nFirst Capitol Consulting, with its professionals with deep roots in mergers and acquisitions, assisted the acquired company and the shareholders to tax minimization.  ', 'Cosmetic', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '99-revision-5', '', '', '2012-12-24 21:01:14', '2012-12-24 21:01:14', '', 99, 'http://10.0.1.19:8888/fcci/99-revision-5/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
