(525, 1, '2012-12-06 17:35:26', '2012-12-06 17:35:26', 'Simplicity, Scalability, Mobility - First Capitol Consulting brings you big firm expertise combined with a personal level of service you need and deserve.\r\n\r\n \r\n\r\nEarning tax credits and incentives is not an easy task. Though many accountants and business owners know about them, few are able to claim tax credits to the fullest extent because of the subject area knowledge required to negotiate all the bureaucratic hurdles in the way. First Capitol Consulting focuses solely on tax credits and incentives, which means it is completely focused on optimizing clients’ tax benefits. Our entire team is dedicated to maximizing credit generation. First Capitol Consulting maintains a diverse client portfolio ranging from small, single owner businesses to national Fortune 500 companies; we help businesses of all sizes and types. At the same time, the First Capitol Consulting team is comprised of professionals from the “Big 4” accounting firms. Hence, we offer the highest level of expertise and experience.\r\n\r\nThe tax credit generating process is specialized, which generally deters businesses from utilizing such programs. Moreover, generating credits requires consistent managing, long term oversight and maintenance. Non-specialists are not able to compete with our expertise to effectively generate tax credits.\r\n\r\nFirst Capitol Consulting can ensure you are getting all of the government sanctioned tax benefits your business earns with minimal involvement for you or your accountant.', 'TaxAdvantage<sup>sm</sup> Competitive Edge', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '17-revision-4', '', '', '2012-12-06 17:35:26', '2012-12-06 17:35:26', '', 17, 'http://10.0.1.19:8888/fcci/17-revision-4/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
