(624, 1, '2012-12-18 06:16:09', '2012-12-18 06:16:09', 'The CAEZ has been in existence since 1984. In addition to its specialized nature, there is generally low awareness about the program because eligible areas have changed over time and the government has not done a good job keeping business owners apprised of all the changes.', 'Why haven''t I heard of CAEZ, WOTC or any of the other tax credit programs before?', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '260-revision-2', '', '', '2012-12-18 06:16:09', '2012-12-18 06:16:09', '', 260, 'http://10.0.1.19:8888/fcci/260-revision-2/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
