(672, 1, '2012-12-25 09:13:50', '2012-12-25 09:13:50', '<h4><i>Because it’s a solution tailored for you!</i></h4>\r\n\r\nFirst Capitol Consulting, inc. was founded in 1999, and has attracted and benefited thousands of\r\ninternational and national brands, fortune 500 companies, and small to mid-sized businesses to\r\nhelp optimize their tax credits.\r\n\r\nOur professional staff is comprised of tax professionals from the "Big 4" accounting firms, and\r\nwas created to provide more personalized, focused, and consistent professional services than\r\nwhat is possible at those “Big 4” accounting firms.\r\n\r\nWe believe that the need to be successful is universal, but how each client gets there is unique.\r\nOur services are not just a “one-size-fits-all” solution - we forge a personalized relationship with\r\neach of our clients and commit to fully understanding your industry and special needs. This\r\nallows us to ensure that your tax incentive program is tailored to your unique situation to provide\r\nyou with the highest amounts of tax credits available to you.\r\n\r\nTo maintain our competitive edge, we partnered with Intuit in 2008 to co-develop our proprietary\r\nweb platform, IT solutions, and call-center. We combined them with our tax professionals to\r\nimplement Work Opportunity Tax Credit (WOTC) and California Enterprise Zone (CAEZ) tax\r\nprograms. The TaxAdvantagesm web portal provides our clients with online employee screening\r\ncapabilities and up-to-date information on their credit program. This process is built to handle\r\nover 1.4 million companies with unlimited number of employees in a transparent, robust and userfriendly\r\nenvironment. TaxAdvantagesm is scalable, simple, and free of upfront or hidden costs.', 'Why TaxAdvantage<sup>SM</sup>', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '11-revision-12', '', '', '2012-12-25 09:13:50', '2012-12-25 09:13:50', '', 11, 'http://10.0.1.19:8888/fcci/11-revision-12/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(673, 1, '2012-12-27 00:27:34', '2012-12-27 00:27:34', '<h4><i>Because it’s a solution tailored for you!</i></h4>\r\n\r\nFirst Capitol Consulting, inc. was founded in 1999, and has attracted and benefited thousands of\r\ninternational and national brands, fortune 500 companies, and small to mid-sized businesses to\r\nhelp optimize their tax credits.\r\n\r\nOur professional staff is comprised of tax professionals from the "Big 4" accounting firms, and was created to provide more personalized, focused, and consistent professional services than what is possible at those “Big 4” accounting firms.\r\n\r\nWe believe that the need to be successful is universal, but how each client gets there is unique. Our services are not just a “one-size-fits-all” solution - we forge a personalized relationship with each of our clients and commit to fully understanding your industry and special needs. This allows us to ensure that your tax incentive program is tailored to your unique situation to provide you with the highest amounts of tax credits available to you.\r\n\r\nTo maintain our competitive edge, we partnered with Intuit in 2008 to co-develop our proprietary web platform, IT solutions, and call-center. We combined them with our tax professionals to implement Work Opportunity Tax Credit (WOTC) and California Enterprise Zone (CAEZ) tax programs. The TaxAdvantagesm web portal provides our clients with online employee screening capabilities and up-to-date information on their credit program. This process is built to handle over 1.4 million companies with unlimited number of employees in a transparent, robust and user-friendly environment. TaxAdvantagesm is scalable, simple, and free of upfront or hidden costs.', 'Why TaxAdvantage<sup>SM</sup>', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '11-revision-13', '', '', '2012-12-27 00:27:34', '2012-12-27 00:27:34', '', 11, 'http://10.0.1.19:8888/fcci/11-revision-13/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(674, 1, '2012-12-25 09:18:25', '2012-12-25 09:18:25', '<h4><i>Simple. Scalable. Mobile.</i></h4>\r\n\r\nFirst Capitol Consulting, Inc. brings you “big firm” expertise, combined with a personal level of\r\nservice you need and deserve.\r\n\r\nWe all know that earning tax credits and incentives is not an easy task. Even though many\r\naccountants and business owners know about them, few are able to claim tax credits to the fullest\r\nextent because of the subject area knowledge that is required to negotiate all the bureaucratic\r\nhurdles thrown your way. We focus solely on tax credits and incentives, which means we are\r\ncompletely focused on optimizing clients’ tax benefits.\r\n\r\nOur entire team is dedicated to maximizing credit generation. We maintain a diverse client\r\nportfolio ranging from small, single owner businesses to national Fortune 500 companies; we help\r\nbusinesses of all sizes and types. At the same time, our team is comprised of professionals from\r\nthe “Big 4” accounting firms. Hence, we offer the highest level of expertise and experience.\r\nThe tax credit generating process is specialized, which generally deters businesses from utilizing\r\nsuch programs. Moreover, generating credits requires consistent managing, long-term oversight\r\nand maintenance. Non-specialists are not able to compete with our expertise to effectively\r\ngenerate tax credits.\r\n\r\nFirst Capitol Consulting, Inc. can ensure you are getting all of the government sanctioned tax\r\nbenefits your business earns with minimal involvement for you or your accountant.', 'TaxAdvantage<sup>sm</sup> &mdash; Competitive Edge', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '17-revision-9', '', '', '2012-12-25 09:18:25', '2012-12-25 09:18:25', '', 17, 'http://10.0.1.19:8888/fcci/17-revision-9/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(675, 1, '2012-12-25 21:39:18', '2012-12-25 21:39:18', '<h4><i>Because you deserve the expertise and communication required to manage the multistage,\r\ntime-sensitive federal and state tax credit claims.</i></h4>\r\n\r\n<p>TaxAdvantagesm streamlines the credit generation process by combining federal and state tax\r\ncredit capture. Through consolidation, TaxAdvantage<sup>sm</sup> offers:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>The capture of time-sensitive overlapping state and federal tax credits</li>\r\n<li>Reduced client overhead.</li>\r\n<li>Better coordination and direct communication with our senior tax professionals through\r\nour web portal.</li>\r\n<li>Representation with the IRS and state taxing authorities by tax professionals from the\r\n"Big 4" accounting firms.</li>\r\n<li>Maximized state tax credits via utilization of the web portal, web integration and call\r\ncenter data capture.</li>\r\n</ul>', 'Why sign up?', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '14-revision-11', '', '', '2012-12-25 21:39:18', '2012-12-25 21:39:18', '', 14, 'http://10.0.1.19:8888/fcci/14-revision-11/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
