(688, 1, '2012-12-26 01:24:13', '2012-12-26 01:24:13', '<h2>Overview</h2>\r\n\r\nFirst Capitol Consulting, Inc. has strong presence in the automotive industry. We currently represent a regional automotive company with over $2.5 billion in assets.\r\n\r\n<h2>Company Profile</h2>\r\n\r\nAs one of the fastest growing automotive companies in the country, this company needed assistance with federal tax credit programs. They were very disenchanted with their prior service provider''s antiquated process, non-intuitive methodology and lack of tax knowledge.\r\n\r\n<h2>Tax Savings</h2>\r\n\r\nFirst Capitol Consulting, Inc. utilized its call-center and web integrated portal to capture federal tax credits. Our process resulted in a 147% increase in hiring tax credits compared to previous year completed by a publicly traded tax credit company.', 'Automative', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '93-revision-8', '', '', '2012-12-26 01:24:13', '2012-12-26 01:24:13', '', 93, 'http://10.0.1.19:8888/fcci/93-revision-8/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(689, 1, '2012-12-25 23:12:54', '2012-12-25 23:12:54', '<h2>Overview</h2>\r\n\r\nFirst Capitol Consulting, Inc. understands the workings and needs of high-tech companies. In a partnership with Intuit, we developed a proprietary software and web-portal. We understand hightech company initiatives, personnel, and very specific needs.\r\n\r\n<h2>Company Profile</h2>\r\n\r\nIndustry leader and Fortune 500 company that is expanding to other states and countries. Due to its rapid growth, the company used temporary work source via third party temporary workforce agency to meet its rapid growth.\r\n\r\n<h2>Tax Savings</h2>\r\n\r\nFirst Capitol Consulting, Inc.''s understanding of high-tech company operations and hiring practices led to capturing tax credits that were previously overlooked by other credits and incentive providers. By implementing its strategy, we increased federal credits and quadrupled state tax credits, lowering the effective tax rate from 33% to 27.5%.', 'High – Tech Companies', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '89-revision-8', '', '', '2012-12-25 23:12:54', '2012-12-25 23:12:54', '', 89, 'http://10.0.1.19:8888/fcci/89-revision-8/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
